          "                     </div>",
          "-                    <div class=\"insight-description\">",
          "-                        Andrej Karpathy revealed his workflow has dramatically shifted from 80% manual coding + 20% AI assistance to 80% AI + 20% manual editing. One company reported 10-20x faster progress using AI coding tools.",
          "+                    <div class=\"insight-author\">Stanford University</div>",
